  "title": "Finance Assistant",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Scope & Responsibilities – Finance Assistant (Restaurant Operations)</strong></h3><p>Handle daily sales reconciliation, including POS reports, cash, and card settlements</p><p>Prepare and process supplier invoices, staff claims, and payments</p><p>Monitor and record daily revenue, expenses, and petty cash for restaurant outlets</p><p>Assist with accounts payable and accounts receivable functions</p><p>Track food cost, beverage cost, and operating expenses</p><p>Support stock and inventory reporting in coordination with kitchen and outlet teams</p><p>Assist in bank reconciliations and monthly closing activities</p><p>Prepare basic financial reports for management review</p><p>Ensure proper filing and documentation of financial records</p><p>Support compliance with internal controls, company policies, and regulatory requirements</p><p>Liaise with outlet managers, suppliers, and external parties when required<br /><br />Assist with work pass applications and related administrative documentation</p><p>Perform other ad-hoc finance and administrative duties related to restaurant operations</p>",
